description: I was so happy to find a cutie willing to talk. You can imagine how thrilled I was when he told me there was a friend waiting for him in a nearby pub. In the Czech Republic, the best way to make new friends is to buy them drinks. That always works. The boys were both unemployed and really sad that they couldn´t afford a nice holiday abroad. My wallet cheered them up a bit. We fooled around but they were really shy, weirdly enough, they preferred to go to my friend´s flat than do stuff in public. I wanted to help them but a holiday abroad can be very expensive. They had to earn the money hard. And I cannot picture them lying on the beach sipping some nice and cool cocktails. But they definitely need some relax after having my juicy dick in their tight virgin holes.
title: Czech Hunter 257
